<l>pullā tirāap pulattai yavaruṟum </l>
<l> allalyāṅ kāṇkañ ciṟitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let us witness awhile his keen suffering just feign dislike and embrace him not.</l>
